      <title>德国央行在“疲软”经济中对商业地产保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bundesbank-vigilant-on-commercial-property-in-weak-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，在经济前景不佳的情况下，金融监管机构正在密切关注银行和投资者在商业地产方面面临的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bundesbank-vigilant-on-commercial-property-in-weak-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
